ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I think this class is very beneficial for me to reflect on my own teaching methods and improve my teaching skills in my future career. I will definitely recommend this class to another student.
I would recommend LING 564 to a fellow student as valuable pedagogical training.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class is directly related to my teaching career. Next semester I will work as an assistant instructor of Chinese language again. I will be able to apply the theories of second language acquisition in my teaching.
